text: Roseburg is a city in the U.S. state of Oregon.Entry for Roseburg in the Oregon Blue Book According to the U.S. Census, 23,683 people lived in Roseburg in 2020. On 1 October 2015, a gunman killed twelve people and injured twenty others at Umpqua Community College in Roseburg. ==References== Category:Cities in Oregon Category:County seats in Oregon
